{"tid":1884980,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"撐警大聯盟政總聲討港台 大家入黎一齊做","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T11:22:52.000Z","uid":259882,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"28f610273ad649d40aa33793848a0f0776dee3b2","tid":1884980,"uid":259882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:23:29.000Z","msg":"撐警大聯盟政總聲討港台<br />\n1. 港台路線正確, 覺得港台條片上到熱門. 意識形態有機會去到淺藍, 威脅政權. 得閒既可以寫信/email 去支持港台 (凡敵人反對的, 你知道的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n2. 敵人想港台同黃KOL都冇錢賺, 首先攬炒藍KOL (下面有link)<br />\n3. 最最最緊要係咩, like + subscribe + click 鐘仔 + share<br />\n4. (自選) 金主可以落廣告/開patreon/課金/搞活動, 自由發揮<br />\n<br />\n頭條新聞 (未睇快D睇, 已經俾人report 到restricted, 公司睇唔到 =.=)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cZB5OsiPcJI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcZB5OsiPcJI&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=1cfb79b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cZB5OsiPcJI</a><br />\n小豪子與志森<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jCGTT2DMHzY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjCGTT2DMHzY&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=cd740816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jCGTT2DMHzY</a><br />\n同場加映 arm channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9MDotjnYPTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9MDotjnYPTY&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=49c9d42b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9MDotjnYPTY</a><br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\nReport 到你臭街<br />\n「資訊戰」有個痴線佬準備好曬中宣部旗下youtuber既report link<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1883056/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1883056/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e30833cbd7d189f7e408ccc714da412bae4c1bf5","tid":1884980,"uid":2598